The history of the
Mongols was written by

00:00:50.950 --> 00:00:53.453
historians like Rashid Al-Din,
from the 17th century.

00:00:53.453 --> 00:00:55.021
He wrote about this place.

00:00:55.021 --> 00:00:57.423
They wanted to go here
but they couldn't.

00:00:57.423 --> 00:01:00.360
And for the first time,
I am entering into this zone.

00:01:02.862 --> 00:01:04.630
<i> I am on that journey.</i>

