And the result is you
create these maps of

00:01:38.497 --> 00:01:39.765
what's under the
sub-surface, right.

00:01:39.765 --> 00:01:44.137
<i> There is some metal underneath
 this rectangular mound.</i>

00:01:44.137 --> 00:01:46.171
<i> We don't really know what
 it was but it wasn't--</i>

00:01:46.171 --> 00:01:47.373
<i> we don't believe
 it was, you know</i>

00:01:47.373 --> 00:01:49.409
<i> what we were really
 looking for.</i>

00:01:50.343 --> 00:01:51.844
<i> So we push north,
 we push deeper</i>

00:01:51.844 --> 00:01:53.912
<i> into this region of
 this Ikh Khorig</i>

00:01:53.912 --> 00:01:55.215
<i> towards this mountain, right.</i>

00:01:55.215 --> 00:01:58.517
<i> This place that legend has
 it Genghis Khan went to</i>

00:01:58.517 --> 00:02:00.419
<i> every time he went
 to war, right.</i>

