He'd go there and
pray to Tengri and say

00:02:03.623 --> 00:02:07.293
well, you know,
"Am I okay here".

00:02:07.293 --> 00:02:09.762
Then he would go
out and wage war.

00:02:09.762 --> 00:02:11.831
<i> We would head out
 every single day</i>

